claim.claim-text:
1. A method for a professional to attract clients by marketing to those who have no prior professional relationship with said professional, comprising the steps of: 
(a) providing at no charge to a public user, the use of an expert system; 
(b) said expert system providing a Professional End Product in response to said user's input; 
(c) providing means for facilitating said user's communication with said professional; 
(d) inviting said user to communicate with said professional to discuss the provision of professional services for a fee.
